      <title>人工智能带动中国智能手机市场反弹，高通股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，高通股价在盘前交易中上涨 4%，此前这家专注于智能手机的芯片制造商表示，在经历了两年的低迷之后，人工智能推动的需求出现反弹，尤其是在中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
