      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-summons-chinese-diplomat-over-south-china-sea-flare-up-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周四召见一名中国外交官，抗议北京在南海争议浅滩对菲律宾船只使用高压水枪，称其为骚扰和“危险举动”。]]></description>
